{"tid":486034,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇睇過《誣網》哩套電影?","createTime":"2017-12-01T12:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T05:19:51.000Z","uid":37708,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25557441537bdacdb2ef03805a8aac462cf0bf34","tid":486034,"uid":37708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"《誣網》(丹麥語：Jagten) 是一部2012年湯瑪士&middot;溫德堡導演的丹麥電影，麥斯&middot;米基辛主演。為第65屆康城國際影展的主競賽片[1][2]。本片代表丹麥角逐第86屆奧斯卡最佳外語片。<br />\n<br />\n劇情:<br />\nLucas是丹麥小鎮上一所幼兒園的教師，由於一個小女孩Klara（Lucas好友、鄰居的女兒）對園長撒謊稱她看到了Lucas的性器官，於是Lucas被懷疑認為是性侵了小孩子，消息傳開後他就因此遭到了該鎮居民的排擠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/205844_44036a5253495749185af841abed2198.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F205844_44036a5253495749185af841abed2198.jpg&h=5b8f1781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推介大家睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1402f20cfbbab10d67ac46cfe6921db4276cce26","tid":486034,"uid":6436,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"推薦俾所有香港人睇"},{"pid":"22df6af541e517da653b3eb9063b2c9b78267b80","tid":486034,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301be9fd1fce4ef5db892b45d53190f438198a06","tid":486034,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推薦俾所有香港人睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf72a5179c597d734593e2a57de382b6b77c91ee","tid":486034,"uid":55991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:15:14.000Z","msg":"睇過 最後個伏筆幾正"},{"pid":"fb73666fa7604059cc5f7a83af15adc8f418de1d","tid":486034,"uid":154684,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"主角慘到仆街<br />\n就算還左佢清白, 陰影都跟一世"},{"pid":"2673bcaa00ffd114a503d347dd0d20f72810613a","tid":486034,"uid":37708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8966509fdf0789d1df1abbf27a5d4c7ebf5f35","tid":486034,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed819a73d3f9e6c85853787564e355bff8b48fc","tid":486034,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"記得睇埋導演舊作the celebration"},{"pid":"c63f5bd2230249e7c3df60702538707b4c56ef56","tid":486034,"uid":124951,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"同近排呂麗瑤單野襯到絕"},{"pid":"e850575c834da8957c312bdd791df6adf236549f","tid":486034,"uid":124951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"呢套野真係好好睇,但絕對唔會想睇第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主角實在太慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣睇到成肚火,好想走入套戲入面打柒鎮上班仆街同個細路女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5bb64747efcf88aca27857d94accd2dc146e89","tid":486034,"uid":145923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"值得一看"},{"pid":"952a8cb048a67459c6e9f6fc4b94ed767ff5b53d","tid":486034,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得睇埋導演舊作the celebration</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor